author: Tesla
description:
Megapack grid-forming inverters are key to enabling global grid stability and reliability. Megan Jackson, Tesla Sr Sales Engineering Manager explains how this technology works, creating its own voltage signal, preventing blackouts and allowing more renewables to come online. The Koorangie Battery Energy Storage System in Australia was developed by Edify and is owned by Sosteneo.

Learn more – https://www.tesla.com/megapack
title: Forming the Future Grid | Tesla Megapack
